California Metal is the first of five compilation albums released by Regency Records in the late 1980's. Many, if not all, of the tracks on the album are unavailable elsewhere.

[edit] Track listing

   1. Barren Cross - "Deadlock" (4:13)
   2. Guardian - "Marching On" (3:38)
   3. Neon Cross - "I Need Your Love" (3:06)
   4. Hero - "I Surrender" (3:47)
   5. Deliverance - "A Space Called You" (3:51)
   6. Mastedon - "Wasn't It Love" (4:42)
      by John & Dino Elefante
      not available elsewhere
   7. Guardian - "Spiritual Warfare" (4:13)
   8. Deliverance - "Attack" (3:44)
   9. Hero - "Sing It Out" (3:02)
  10. Neon Cross - "Son of God" (4:16)
